OL,3,CPlanning approved for #231 million
OL,4,CBarbican Centre renewal
OL,6,FThe City of London Corporation has
OL,7,Fapproved a #231 million renewal plan
OL,8,Ffor the Barbican Centre.The multi-arts
OL,9,Fcentre will see a number of
OL,10,Fmaintenance and accessibility issues
OL,11,Faddressed under its newly approved
OL,12,FBarbican Renewal Programme.
OL,14,FThe programme will see a new lift and
OL,15,Fstaircase installed in the
OL,16,Fconservatory, offering public access
OL,17,Fto its raised balconies, as well as
OL,18,Fintroducing a climate-controlled
OL,19,Fhabitat to support plant health.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
