CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772561166
OL,3,CPlanning approved for #231 million
OL,4,CBarbican Centre renewal
OL,6,FThe renewal will also see a second
OL,7,Flift installed in the main foyer to
OL,8,Fenhance accessibility to the concert
OL,9,Fhall theatre and surrounding spaces
OL,10,Falong with a new multi-faith room,
OL,11,Fincreased toilet provision and step-
OL,12,Ffree access throughout the site.
OL,14,FThe Barbican's distinctive Brutalist
OL,15,Ffoyers and lakeside terrace will also
OL,16,Fbe developed to protect the heritage
OL,17,Fof the Grade II-listed building.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
