CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772561166
OL,3,CPlanning approved for #231 million
OL,4,CBarbican Centre renewal
OL,6,F"By backing it with significant
OL,7,Finvestment, we're driving jobs,
OL,8,Fboosting the city's economy, and
OL,9,Fstrengthening its reputation as a
OL,10,Fmagnet for visitors, talent, and
OL,11,Faudiences from across the globe.
OL,13,F"Just as importantly, we're
OL,14,Ftransforming the centre so it's open,
OL,15,Faccessible and ready for the future."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@eO]
