OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772561166
OL,3,CPlanning approved for #231 million
OL,4,CBarbican Centre renewal
OL,6,FThe City Corporation has committed
OL,7,F#191 million towards the #231 million
OL,8,Fneeded to complete the first phase of
OL,9,Fthe Barbican renewal programme with
OL,10,Fthe remaining funds sought through
OL,11,Fphilanthropic and partnership support.
OL,13,FOpened in 1982 by the late Queen
OL,14,FElizabeth II, the Barbican is one of
OL,15,Fthe largest performing arts centres in
OL,16,FEurope and draws in millions of
OL,17,Fvisitors each year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
