PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772561166
OL,3,CPlanning approved for #231 million
OL,4,CBarbican Centre renewal
OL,6,FPhilippa Simpson, Barbican Centre
OL,7,Fchief operating officer, said: "We're
OL,8,Fthrilled that phase 1 of Barbican
OL,9,FRenewal has been approved.
OL,11,F"Securing planning permission and
OL,12,Flisted building consent allows us to
OL,13,Frestore, celebrate and revitalise the
OL,14,FBarbican Centre, so we can continue to
OL,15,Fdeliver a dynamic, world-class arts
OL,16,Fprogramme and provide the best
OL,17,Fpossible welcome to new and existing
OL,18,Fvisitors.
OL,26,@oD@`OUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
