OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772561166
OL,3,CPlanning approved for #231 million
OL,4,CBarbican Centre renewal
OL,6,F"This programme invests in the whole
OL,7,Flife of the centre. It will improve
OL,8,Faccess, release spaces for public use,
OL,9,Fand support ambitious artistic work at
OL,10,Fevery scale.
OL,12,F"This decision secures this visionary
OL,13,Fplace of art and encounter for future
OL,14,Fgenerations and will help us expand
OL,15,Four reach nationally and
OL,16,Finternationally."
OL,18,FThe design team delivering the
OL,19,Fprogramme is led by Allies & Morrison
OL,20,Fworking with Asif Khan Studio and
OL,21,Fengineers Buro Happold.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@QO]
